# Project-specific ignored files
.design_docs/
.tmp/
.codex
# Wails-generated TS bindings for the desktop App methods. NOT ignored
# (intentionally tracked) so CI's `tsc --noEmit` step can resolve the
# imports without needing to install the Wails CLI and regenerate. The
# files are regenerated on every `make desktop-build`; a stale entry
# here will show up as a diff and prompt re-running the build.
cmd/downstage-write/frontend/*
!cmd/downstage-write/frontend/.gitkeep
cmd/downstage-write/build/
